e":161,"tagline":"Something evil has returned to Hogwarts!","homepage":"https://www.warnerbros.com/movies/harry-potter-and-chamber-secrets","overview":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione's magical abilities and courage."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter und die Kammer des Schreckens","runtime":161,"tagline":"Hogwarts ist zurück!","homepage":"https://www.warnerbros.de/filme/harry-potter-und-die-kammer-des-schreckens","overview":"Harry Potter könnte sich schönere Sommerferien vorstellen: Einerseits erträgt er nur schwer den herrischen Ton im Haus von Tante Petunia und Onkel Vernon Dursley, denen seine Zauberkunst nicht geheuer ist, andererseits haben ihn seine besten Freunde Ron Weasley und Hermine Granger offenbar vergessen, denn sie beantworten keinen seiner Briefe. Plötzlich taucht der geheimnisvolle Haus-Elf Dobby in Harrys Schlafzimmer auf und warnt ihn: Falls Harry nach Hogwarts zurückkehrt, schwebt er in großer Gefahr. Dobby will den jungen Gryffindor unbedingt davon abhalten, weiter auf die Schule für Hexerei und Zauberei zu gehen – deswegen hat er dafür gesorgt, dass Rons und Hermines Briefe nicht ankommen. Doch was der boshafte Elf auch anstellt – Harry lässt sich nicht beirren."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter ja salaisuuksien kammio","runtime":162,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Autot lentävät, puut taistelevat vastaan ja salaperäinen tonttu varoittaa Harry Potteria hänen jatkaessaan uskomatonta matkaansa taikuuden maailmassa. Tänä vuonna Tylypahkassa hämähäkit puhuvat, kirjeet toruvat ja Harryn pelottava taito puhua käärmeille kääntää hänen ystävänsä häntä vastaan. Kaksintaistelukerhosta villeihin ryhmyihin tämä kouluvuosi on täynnä seikkailuja ja vaaroja kun verinen teksti seinällä julistaa: Salaisuuksien kammio on avattu. Tylypahkan pelastaminen vaatii Harryn, Ronin ja Hermionen kaiken rohkeuden ja taikakeinot tässä…"},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter e la camera dei segreti","runtime":161,"tagline":"Qualcosa di oscuro è tornato ad Hogwarts","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter sta trascorrendo noiose vacanze estive presso gli zii, oltretutto senza aver ricevuto nemmeno un messaggio dagli amici Ron e Hermione. Colpa di Dobby, elfo domestico che ha intercettato la posta per convincere il ragazzo a lasciare la scuola di magia di Hogwarts dove lo attenderebbe un terribile pericolo. L'arrivo all'accademia coincide in effetti con una serie di strani e paurosi fenomeni: esseri pietrificati, scritte di sangue sui muri e soprattutto l'accenno a una misteriosa \"camera dei segreti\" che conterrebbe qualcosa di malefico. Quando il pericolo comincerà a riguardare i suoi amici Harry saprà risolvere la situazione."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter e a Câmara dos Segredos","runtime":154,"tagline":"Algo cruel se move em Hogwarts.","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter frequenta o segundo ano de Hogwarts, a escola de bruxarias e feitiços. Ele é visitado por um duende doméstico chamado Dobby que o aconselha a não regressar à escola. Harry ignora este aviso e regressa. Ele continua famoso, mas detestado pelos Slytherins, e ainda mais por Snape e Malfoy. De repente, coisas estranhas começam a acontecer: as pessoas começam a ficar petrificadas e ninguém conhece a causa disso. Entretanto Harry continua a ouvir uma voz... uma voz que parece vir das paredes... lembra-se da história da Câmara dos Segredos, diz-se que só o verdadeiro descendente de Salazar Slytherin será capaz de abri-la..."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter en de Geheime Kamer","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Vlak voor zijn tweede jaar op de Zweinstein School voor Hekserij en Tovenarij wordt tovenaarsleerling Harry Potter door de elf Dobby gewaarschuwd dat zijn terugkeer op de school tot een ramp zal leiden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter és a Titkok kamrája","runtime":161,"tagline":"Valami gonosz visszatért a Roxfortba!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter nyári vakációja nem a legjobban sikerült. Mindezt tetézi, hogy megjelenik nála Dobby, a házimanó, hogy figyelmeztesse, nagy veszély leselkedik rá a Roxfort Boszorkány- és Varázslóképző Szakiskola falai között. Harry és Ron lekési a Roxfort Expresszt, amely visszavinné őket az iskolába, így a repülő autóval indulnak útnak, nehogy elkéssenek az új tanév kezdetéről. Harry csakhamar megint az érdeklődés középpontjában találja magát, ugyanis az iskolában új rajongói akadnak, köztük a Feketemágia-ellenes Liga professzora, Gilderoy Lockhart. Lockhart különös módon egyre gyakrabban mutatkozik Harry társaságában. De még Lockhart sem képes megállítani az új és minden eddiginél gonoszabb hatalmat, amely az iskolát fenyegeti."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter a Tajomná komnata","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter sa po prázdninách vracia do Rokfortu a nastupuje do druhého ročníka. A to i napriek varovaniu domáceho škriatka Dobbyho, podľa ktorého mu v Rokforte hrozí smrť. V škole kúziel a mágie sa však skutočne začnú diať čudné udalosti. Na stenách sa objavujú neznáme nápisy a niektorí študenti sú prepadávaní tajomným prízrakom. Čo s tým má spoločné Tajomná komnata? Stojí za spiknutím opäť Voldemort? Záhadu sa Harry vydáva rozlúštiť spoločne so svojimi priateľmi - Ronom a Hermionou."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Гарри Поттер и Тайная комната","runtime":161,"tagline":"«Зло вернулось в Хогвартс»","homepage":"","overview":"Гарри Поттер переходит на второй курс Школы чародейства и волшебства Хогвартс. Эльф Добби предупреждает Гарри об опасности, которая поджидает его там, и просит больше не возвращаться в школу. Юный волшебник не следует совету эльфа и становится свидетелем таинственных событий, разворачивающихся в Хогвартсе. Вскоре Гарри и его друзья узнают о существовании Тайной Комнаты и сталкиваются с новыми приключениями, пытаясь победить тёмные силы."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter et la Chambre des secrets","runtime":161,"tagline":"Quelque chose de maléfique est de retour à Poudlard !","homepage":"","overview":"Après de très mauvaises vacances passées chez ses odieux oncle et tante et son affreux cousin, Harry rejoint, non sans mal, l'École des Sorciers où, avec ses amis Ron et Hermione et l'aide ponctuelle de nouveaux venus, il parvient à élucider le mystère de la Chambre des secrets, malgré les pièges tendus par ses ennemis et sans le concours de Lockhart, un nouveau professeur fanfaron et lâche, chargé pourtant de vaincre les Forces du Mal."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter och hemligheternas kammare","runtime":162,"tagline":"Någon, eller något, förstenar den ena Hogwarteleven efter den andra.","homepage":"","overview":"Sommarlovet är äntligen över! Harry Potter har längtat tillbaka till sitt andra år på Hogwarts skola för häxkonster och trolldom. Men hur ska han stå ut med den nye, omåttligt mallige professor Lockman? Vad döljer Hagrids förflutna? Och vem är egentligen Missnöjda Myrtle? De verkliga problemen börjar när någon, eller något, förstenar den ena Hogwarteleven efter den andra. Är det Harrys största fiende, Draco Malfoy, som ligger bakom? Eller är det den som alla på Hogwarts misstänker – Harry Potter själv?"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter a Tajemná komnata","runtime":161,"tagline":"Zlo se vrátilo do Bradavic","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter se po prázdninách vrací do Bradavic a nastupuje do druhého ročníku. A to i přes varování domácího skřítka Dobbyho, podle kterého mu v čarodějné škole hrozí smrt. Harry nedbá nářků skřítka působícího víc škody než užitku, ale potom se skutečně začnou dít podivné věci, na stěnách se objevují neznámé nápisy a několik studentů je přepadeno tajemným přízrakem. Co s tím má společného Tajemná komnata? Stojí za spiknutím opět Voldemort? Kdo je Zmijozelův dědic? Záhadu se Harry vydává rozluštit společně se svými starými známými – Ronem a Hermionou."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"哈利·波特与密室","runtime":161,"tagline":"某种邪恶再度回到霍格沃兹","homepage":"","overview":"哈利·波特结束了假期，即将回到霍格沃兹继续学习魔法。然而一个叫多比的家养小精灵出现警告哈利不要回到霍格沃兹，否则会陷入极大的危险。哈利没有听从多比的劝告，回到了霍格沃兹。很快，霍格沃兹发生了一连窜怪事：接二连三出现学生被石化，一直找不出原因。而哈利总能听到一种奇怪的声音，从墙壁里传出来。传说，霍格沃兹有一个密室，里面记录着伏地魔年轻时的秘密，只有斯莱特林的继承人才能打开密室。哈利偶然发现自己能听懂蛇说话，一时传闻是哈利打开了密室。难道多比所指的危险就隐藏在密室？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter ve Sırlar Odası","runtime":175,"tagline":"Hogwarts geri döndü.","homepage":"","overview":"Hogwarts Cadılık ve Büyücülük okulundaki ikinci yılına başlarken Harry Potter, ev cini Dobby tarafından okula dönmesinin kendisi için tehlikeli olacağı konusunda uyarılır. Bunun yanında Profesör Snape ondan halen hoşlanmamaktadır, Draco Malfoy da ondan hala nefret eder. Bu ortamda Harry en iyi arkadaşları Ron ve Hermione ile birlikte yeni bir okul yılına başlar. Ünlü yazar Gilderoy Lockhart da bu yıl Hogwarts'a katılmıştır. Ancak Hogwarts öğrencileri garip bir şekilde taşa dönüşmektedirler. Bunu kimin yaptığıysa gizemini korumaktadır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter y la cámara secreta","runtime":150,"tagline":"¡Algo maligno ha vuelto a Hogwarts!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry regresa a su segundo año a Hogwarts, pero descubre que cosas malas ocurren debido a que un sitio llamado la Cámara de los Secretos ha sido abierto por el heredero de Slytherin y hará que los hijos de muggles, los impuros, aparezcan petrificados misteriosamente por un animal monstruoso."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Ο Χάρι Πότερ και η Κάμαρα με τα Μυστικά","runtime":161,"tagline":"Το κακό επιστρέφει στο Χόγκουαρτς!","homepage":"","overview":"Ο Χάρι επιστρέφει με τους φίλους του Ρόν Ουέσλι και Ερμιόνη Γκρέιντζερ για τον δεύτερο χρόνο τους στην σχολή μαγείας Χόγκουαρντς. Οι τρεις πρωταγωνιστές καλούνται να αντιμετωπίσουν μυστήρια τα οποία ακόμη και οι δάσκαλοι της σχολής μοιάζουν να φοβούνται να αντιμετωπίσουν. Υπάρχει πραγματικά μια Κάμαρα με Μυστικά κρυμμένη κάπου μέσα στο Χόγκουαρντς; Υπάρχει πραγματικά κάποιο τέρας εκεί μέσα; Ή μήπως το τέρας έχει ήδη δραπετεύσει και είναι υπεύθυνο για ότι συμβαίνει στους μαθητές; Οι απαντήσεις βρίσκονται στο παρελθόν, αλλά και στο παρόν και είναι στα χέρια των ηρώων μας να λύσουν και αυτό το μυστήριο."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter og hemmelighedernes kammer","runtime":162,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Unge Harry har taget hul på sit andet år på Hogwarts, trods adskillige advarsler. Det varer ikke længe, før Harry og vennerne opdager, at der er noget helt galt på skolen. Elever bliver forvandlet til sten, trusler bliver skrevet med blod på væggene og et dødbringende monster er løs! Nogen har åbnet Hemmelighedernes Kammer. Harry, Ron og Hermione sætter sig for at finde kammeret og dræbe monstret. Rygtet siger, at Hemmelighedernes Kammer er blevet åbnet af en arvtager til Salazar Slytherin – en af Hogwarts grundlæggere. Mistanken retter sig mod den arrogante elev, Draco Malfoy, men Harry frygter, at hans arvefjende, Voldemort står bag de skræmmende begivenheder."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter i Komnata Tajemnic","runtime":161,"tagline":"Coś złego czai się w Hogwarcie!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry powraca do Hogwartu, aby ponownie zmierzyć się z niebezpieczeństwem tym razem zagrażającym także jego najlepszej przyjaciółce. Podczas drugiego roku pobytu w Szkole Magii i Czarodziejststwa młody Potter spotyka starych wrogów, poznaje nowego nauczyciela, odkrywa w sobie nowe zdolności, unika śmierci z rąk domowego skrzata chcącego za wszelką cenę uratować mu życie i wraz z dwójką swoich przyjaciół: Ronem i Hermioną znów udaje mu się rozwiązać trudną zagadkę."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"แฮร์รี่ พอตเตอร์ กับ ห้องแห่งความลับ","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"พ่อมดน้อย แฮร์รี่ พอตเตอร์ กับเพื่อน ๆเของเขา รอน วีสลีย์ และ.เฮอร์มิออนี่ แกรนเจอร์ พบกับการเผชิญหน้าที่ท้าทายครั้งใหม่ ในปีที่ 2 ของการเข้าเรียนที่โรงเรียนพ่อมด แม่มด และ.เวทย์มนต์ศาสตร์ ฮอกวอร์ตส์ ซึ่งพวกเขาต้องหาทางเผยโฉมพลังมืด ที่สร้างความหวาดกลัวให้กับทั้งโรงเรียน แม้ว่าจะมีภูติประจำบ้านมาปรากฎกายอย่างลึกลับ เพื่อเตือนแฮร์รี่ถึงอันตรายครั้งใหญ่ที่จะเกิดขึ้น ..."},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"הארי פוטר וחדר הסודות","runtime":0,"tagline":"הרוע חזר להוגוורטס!","homepage":"","overview":"לאחר שבילה קיץ משמים בבית דודו ודודתו, מתגעגע הארי לשוב להוגוורטס. אלא שאז מופיע בחדרו שדון מסתורי בשם דובי, המזהיר אותו מסכנות האורבות לו עם פתיחת שנת הלימודים השנייה. כשהלימודים נפתחים, מסר מיסתורי ומאיים מופיע על קירות בית הספר הוגוורטס, שגורם להארי, רון והרמיוני לצאת למסע להרפתקאה מסוכנת."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter i la cambra secreta","runtime":0,"tagline":"La Cambra dels Secrets ha esta Oberta després de cinquanta anys….","homepage":"","overview":"Harry es fa el sord davant el avisos de que no torni a Hogwarts, i quan hi arriba troba que ha sofert una sèrie de misteriosos atacs."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Хари Потер и дворана тајни","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Хари Потер није баш лепо провео лето. Не само да је једва истрпео своју ујну Петунију и ујака Вернона Дурслија већ је и изгледало да су га заборавили његови најбољи пријатељи - Рон Висли и Хермиона Гренџер нису одговорили ни на једно његово писмо. Одједном се у Харијевој соби мистериозно појављује кућни патуљак Доби и упозорава га на велику опасност која га вреба ако се врати у Хогварт, школу за вештичарење и чаробњаштво. Патуљак жели да спречи младе грифиндорце да се врате у Хогварт и зато је онемогућио да се Рон и Хермиона дописују са Харијем. Међутим, упркос Добијевим напорима, Рон са својом браћом \"спасава\" Харија од ујака и ујне, и то уз помоћ летећих кола! Али, Хари и Рон су на сумњив начин спречени да се укрцају у воз за Хогварт. Момци журе како би избегли кашњење на почетак новог семестра и да не би изазвали љутњу професора Снајпа, пошто је он тражио да њих двојица буду избачени из школе након што су у летећем аутомобилу пали на зачарану врбу Хогварта."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"ハリー・ポッターと秘密の部屋","runtime":161,"tagline":"“ドビーめは警告しに参りました。”","homepage":"","overview":"ハリーは学校での最初の１年を終え、夏休みをダーズリー一家のもとで過ごしていた。ハリーが相変わらず意地悪な一家に嫌気がさしていたある日、突然ドビーという“屋敷しもべ妖精”が現れる。ドビーはホグワーツへ戻らないよう警告するが、ハリーはそれを聞かずに、助けに来てくれたロンと共にダーズリー家を抜け出した。そして新学期。晴れて２年生となったハリーとロンは、もうひとりの親友ハーマイオニーとも再会し、いつもの充実した学校生活を送っていたが、やがて校内で不気味な出来事が次々と起こり始める…。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter og mysteriekammeret","runtime":162,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dette skoleåret ved Galtvort byr på snakkende edderkopper og brev som brøler, og Harrys urovekkende evne til å snakke med slanger skaper splid mellom ham og vennene hans. Når en blodig innskrift på veggen forkynner at \"mysteriekammeret er åpnet\", blir det for alvor farlig."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter ja saladuste kamber","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter on suvevaheajal, kui tema juurde ilmub majahaldjas Dobby, kes hoiatab teda, et ta sel aastal tagasi Sigatüüka kooli ei läheks. Hoiatusest hoolimata otsustab Harry tagasi minna ning koos oma sõprade Ron'i  ja Hermione'ga ohtudele vastu astuda. Harry peab toime tulema oma vaenlase Draco Malfoy alatute trikkidega ning avastama, mis on koolis toimuvate salapäraste rünnakute taga."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"해리 포터와 비밀의 방","runtime":160,"tagline":"어둠의 세력이 호그와트로 돌아왔다","homepage":"","overview":"해리 포터에겐 이번 여름방학이 별로 즐겁질 못했다. 마법이라면 질색을 하는 페투니아 이모와 버논 이모부의 구박도 그렇지만, 무엇보다 속상한 건 단짝이었던 론 위즐리와 헤르미온느 그레인저가 그 사이 자신을 까맣게 잊었는지 자신의 편지에 답장 한 통 없다는 것.  그러던 어느날 꼬마 집요정 도비가 해리의 침실에 나타나 뜻밖의 얘기를 한다. 호그와트 마법학교로 돌아가면 무서운 일을 당할 거라는 것. 도비는 해리를 학교에 못 가게 하려고 자신이 여태까지 론과 헤르미온느의 답장을 가로채 왔음을 고백한다. 그러나 도비와 더즐리 가족의 방해에도 불구, 해리는 론과 그의 형제들이 타고 온 하늘을 나는 자동차를 타고 이모집을 탈출, 따뜻한 가족애가 넘치는 론의 집으로 가는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter și Camera Secretelor","runtime":161,"tagline":"Hogwarts se întoarce în sesiune.","homepage":"","overview":"Tânărul vrăjitor Harry Potter și prietenii lui încearcă să descopere o forță care terorizează școala Hogwarts, în al doilea său an de studii."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter e a Câmara Secreta","runtime":161,"tagline":"A Câmara Secreta foi aberta!","homepage":"https://www.warnerbros.com.br/filmes/harry-potter-e-camara-secreta","overview":"Carros voadores, árvores que lutam e um misterioso elfo, com um aviso ainda mais misterioso. Harry Potter está pronto para dar início ao segundo ano de sua maravilhosa jornada no mundo da bruxaria. Em Hogwarts nesse ano, aranhas falam, cartas dão broncas e a habilidade de Harry para falar com cobras voltará contra ele. De clubes de duelo a jogadores de quadribol desonestos, esse será um ano de aventura e perigo para todos. Quando a mensagem sangrenta na parede anuncia que a Câmara Secreta foi aberta, Harry, Rony e Hermione percebem que para salvar Hogwarts será preciso muita mágica e coragem."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Гаррі Поттер і таємна кімната","runtime":0,"tagline":"Зло повернулося до Гоґвортсу!","homepage":"","overview":"Гаррі Поттер провів чергове довге літо із нестерпними Дурслями. Та ось настав час повертатися до школи чарів і чаклунства Гоґвортс на другий навчальний рік. Проте хтось намагається завадити Гаррі потрапити на потяг до школи. І єдиний спосіб дістатись Гоґвортсу – чарівна літаюча машина, яка, на превеликий жаль, врізається в цінне дерево, Войовничу Вербу. Хай би там як, усе це схоже на буденний день у парку в порівняні з тим, що чекає на Гаррі у залах Гоґвортсу: хлопець починає чути моторошні зловісні голоси, що, здається, долинають зі стін. А ще він підозрює, що Драко Мелфой затіяв щось лихе. Незабаром не тільки Гаррі хвилюється через лиховісні події, адже в школі починають відбуватися жахливі речі. Загадково миготять написані кров’ю на стіні слова, проголошуючи: «ТАЄМНУ КІМНАТУ ВІДЧИНЕНО. СТЕРЕЖІТЬСЯ, ВОРОГИ СПАДКОЄМЦЯ!»"},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter et la Chambre des secrets","runtime":161,"tagline":"Quelque chose de maléfique est de retour à Poudlard !","homepage":"","overview":"Alors que l'oncle Vernon, la tante Pétunia et son cousin Dudley reçoivent d'importants invités à dîner, Harry Potter est contraint de passer la soirée dans sa chambre. Dobby, un elfe, fait alors son apparition. Il lui annonce que de terribles dangers menacent l'école de Poudlard et qu'il ne doit pas y retourner en septembre. Harry refuse de le croire. Mais sitôt la rentrée des classes effectuée, ce dernier entend une voix malveillante. Celle-ci lui dit que la redoutable et légendaire Chambre des Secrets est à nouveau ouverte, permettant ainsi à l'héritier de Serpentard de semer le chaos à Poudlard. Les victimes, retrouvées pétrifiées par une force mystérieuse, se succèdent dans les couloirs de l'école, sans que les professeurs - pas même le populaire Gilderoy Lockhart - ne parviennent à endiguer la menace. Aidé de Ron et Hermione, Harry doit agir au plus vite pour sauver Poudlard."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter y la cámara secreta","runtime":161,"tagline":"¡Algo malvado ha regresado a Hogwarts!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry Potter se prepara para ir a Hogwarts cuando recibe a un elfo doméstico llamado Dobby, quién le advierte que corre en un gran peligro. Llegando a la escuela, sucesos inquietantes motiva a Harry y sus amigos, Ron y Hermione, a investigar lo que está sucediendo en Hogwarts."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Хари Потър и стаята на тайните","runtime":142,"tagline":"Завръщане в Хогуортс.","homepage":"","overview":"Колите летят, дърветата отвръщат на удара и един загадъчен домашен дух се появява, за да се опита да попречи на Хари Потър да не попадне за втора поредна година в света на магьосничеството. Този път в Хогуортс паяците говорят, писмата четата конско, а способността на Хари да общува със змии настройва приятелите му срещу него. Кървав надпис на стената предупреждава: Стаята на тайните е отворена. Хари, Рон и Хърмаяни ще имат нужда от всички свои магически способности и много смелост, за да спасят училището за магии."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter en de geheime kamer","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"беларуская мова","iso_639_1":"be","iso_3166_1":"BY","english_name":"Belarusian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter i Odaja tajni","runtime":0,"tagline":"Nešto zlo se vratilo u Hogwarts!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry se vraća na svoju drugu godinu u Hogwartsu, ali otkriva da se loše događaju jer je Slytherin nasljednik otvorio mjesto pod nazivom Komora tajni i učinit će da se Mugglesova djeca, nečista, očigledno očiste monstruozne životinje."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Haris Poteris ir paslapčių kambarys","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Šiame pasakiškame filme Haris Poteris jau bus visiems pažįstamas Hogvartso antrametis ir susidurs su dar keistesniais padarais bei patirs dar nuostabesnių nuotykių… Sužinosite, kokios liūdnos buvo Hario atostogos pas nedorėlius Durslius, kaip jo neleido grįžti į mokyklą, kaip senutėliu skraidančiu automobiliu jį stebuklingai į Hogvartsą nuskraidino draugai. Na, o ten, žinoma, naujos mįslės.  Kažkas atidarė Paslapčių kambarį, apipintą šiurpiomis legendomis, ir iš ten ištrūkęs monstras keletą mokinių sustingdė į akmenis. Mokyklai gresia uždarymas, iš jos pašalinamas Dumbldoras, suimamas Hagridas… Tačiau Hariui su Roniu pavyksta atrasti Paslapčių kambarį ir atskleisti jo paslaptis bei nugalėti baisių įvykių kaltininką ir laimėti Grifų Gūžtai net 400 taškų!"},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"哈利波特：消失的密室","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"哈利波特的暑假一點也不好過，不僅要忍受蠻橫的佩妮姨媽（費歐娜蕭）和維農德思禮姨丈（李查葛瑞夫斯），還有德思禮一家人對他魔法的恐懼，他的好友榮恩衛斯理和妙麗格蘭傑也似乎忘了他，連一封信也沒有回給他。接著，家庭精靈多比又突然間神秘地出現在哈利的臥房裡，警告哈利波特如果回到了霍格華茲，他就會有立即的生命危險。 多比急著想阻止這位葛來分多的學生回到魔法與巫術學院，甚至攔截了榮恩和妙麗寫給哈利的所有信件，但是僅管有這個精靈來攪局，榮恩和他的幾個哥哥還是把意志堅定的哈利，從德思禮家人的魔掌中救了出來，開著一輛會飛的車子，接到衛斯理有點破舊卻充滿溫暖的家中。 到了開學當天，哈利和榮恩竟然進不了九又四分之三月台，無法搭上霍格華茲特快車的哈利與榮恩，只好偷開榮恩爸爸的飛天魔法車火速趕往學園，以免趕不上新學期的開學典禮，結果卻撞壞了珍貴的渾拼柳，讓石內卜教授大發雷霆，差點將他們趕出校園。 哈利擊退佛地魔王的英勇事蹟，讓他成了全校師生矚目的焦點，就連榮恩的妹妹金妮（邦妮萊特飾）也對他崇拜有加，但是新來的黑魔法防禦術教授吉德羅洛哈（肯尼斯布萊納飾）也不是省油的燈。他可是連續榮獲「女巫周刊最迷人笑容獎」五週冠軍得主，他的出現搶盡了哈利的風采。 今年的魁地奇球賽也出現葛來分多與史萊哲林的兩大世仇對決的精采比賽，史萊哲林全面更新裝備，新掃帚「光輪2001」的優越性能完全打敗哈利波特去年風光一時的「光輪2000」，史萊哲林站了完全的上風，葛來分多面臨兵敗如山倒的危機，哈利能不能夠扭轉逆勢，為葛來分多爭光？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter og leyniklefinn","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harry snýr aftur á annað árið sitt í Hogwarts, en uppgötvar að slæmir hlutir eru að gerast vegna þess að síða sem kallast Leyndarmálaráðherrann hefur verið opnuð af erfingja Slytherin og mun láta börn Muggles, sem eru óhrein, virðast dularfullt steingerving af klaustra dýri."},"name":"Íslenska","iso_639_1":"is","iso_3166_1":"IS","english_name":"Icelandic"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter in dvorana skrivnosti","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harry se vrne v svoje drugo leto v Hogwartsu, vendar odkrije, da se dogajajo slabe stvari, ker je Slytherin dedič odprl mesto, imenovano Zbornica skrivnosti, zaradi česar bodo Mogljevi otroci, nečisti, videti skrivnostno okameneli pošastno žival."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter og mysteriekammeret","runtime":162,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Med trusler mot livet sitt, vender Harry tilbake til Galtvort for å undersøke - med hjelp av av Ronny og Hermine - en mystisk serie angrep."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter và Căn Phòng Bí Mật","runtime":0,"tagline":"Thế lực hắc ám trở lại Hogwarts!","homepage":"","overview":"Harry trở lại năm thứ hai tại Hogwarts, nhưng phát hiện ra rằng những điều tồi tệ đang xảy ra bởi vì một trang web có tên là Phòng chứa bí mật đã được người thừa kế của Slytherin mở ra và sẽ khiến những đứa trẻ của Muggles, những kẻ không trong sạch, xuất hiện một cách bí ẩn bởi một con vật quái dị."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"هری پاتر و تالار اسرار","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"هری پاتر دومين سال تحصيلی‌اش را در مدرسه جادوگری هاگوارتز شروع می‌کند اما يک موجود اسرار آميز در مدرسه در کمين اوست. صداهای شيطانی از ديوارها بگوش می‌رسند و حوادث وحشتناکی در هاگوارتز اتفاق می‌افتد."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter e a Cámara dos Segredos","runtime":160,"tagline":"Algo maligno retornou a Hogwarts","homepage":"","overview":"De vacacións na casa dos tíos, Harry Potter recibe a inesperada visita de Dobby, un elfo doméstico que o vén avisar para non voltar á Escola de Hogwarts. Harry non lle dá importancia e decide voltar. Mais hai novidades á espera e unha delas é a contratación do novo profesor Gilderoy Lockhart, un grande galán que non perde unha oportunidade de falar de si mesmo. Porém, a paz da escola vai ser ensombrada por un misterio que retorna á época da súa propia fundación."},"name":"Galego","iso_639_1":"gl","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Galician"},{"data":{"title":"Harijs Poters un noslēpumu kambaris","runtime":160,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Harijam Poteram vasaras brīvdienas nav nekādas jaukās. Tante Petūnija un tēvocis Vernons viņu necieš ne acu galā. Viņa draugi - Hermione Greindžera un Rons Vīzlijs nav atbildējuši ne uz vienu no Harija vēstulēm. Visbeidzot, Harija istabā uzrodas mājas elfs Dobijs un brīdina Hariju nedoties atpakaļ uz Cūkkārpas skolu, lai uzsāktu otro skolas gadu, jo tur viņu sagaidot lielas briesmas.  Par spīti Dobija centieniem aizturēt Hariju, viņš dodas uz Cūkkārpu, kur kopā ar draugiem cenšas atklāt ļauno spēku, kas ir apsēdis skolu un terorizē tās iedzīvotājus."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"哈利波特：消失的密室","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"新的學年，哈利波特(丹尼爾韋基夫飾)在霍格華茲魔法校園內遇到重重危機; 多比精靈雖然多次阻止哈利返回學校，但哈利與榮恩最後仍能駕駛飛車趕返校園。  在校內接二連三發生意外，學生相繼被石化，牆上亦被塗抹著幾行字跡「密室已經打開。傳人的仇敵們，當心了。」而哈利因為能夠講蛇語更被同學懷疑是那個傳人…哈利今次所面對的黑暗邪惡勢力，表現出他不只是一個出色的魔法師，他還是一位英雄!"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ჰარი პოტერი და საიდუმლო ოთახი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Harry Potter eta Sekretuen Ganbera","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Uda amaiturik, Harryk bere osaba-izeben etxe itogarritik alde egiteko abagunerik ez du aurkitzen. Halako batean Dobby azalduko zaio logelan, elfo domestikoa. Honek ohartarazpen beldurgarria egingo dio: Hogwartsera itzuliko balitz egundoko arriskupean egongo litzateke. Elforen ahaleginak ahalegin, Ron eta bere anaiek auto hegalari batez erreskatatuko dute Harry, zeina Weasleytarren etxe goxoan besozabalik hartuko duten."},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"هاري بوتر و حجرة الأسرار","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.warnerbros.com/movies/harry-potter-and-chamber-secrets","overview":"السيارات تطير ، والأشجار تقاوم ، ويأتي قزم منزل غامض لتحذير هاري بوتر في بداية سنته الثانية في هوجورتس.  تنتظر المغامرة والخطر عندما تعلن كتابة دموية على الحائط: تم فتح غرفة الأسرار.  سيتطلب إنقاذ هوجورتس كل شجاعة وشجاعة هاري ورون وهيرميون السحرية."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mobil terbang, pepohonan melawan, dan peri rumah misterius datang untuk memperingatkan Harry Potter di awal tahun keduanya di Hogwarts. Petualangan dan bahaya menanti ketika tulisan berdarah di dinding mengumumkan: Kamar Rahasia Telah Dibuka. Untuk menyelamatkan Hogwarts akan membutuhkan semua kemampuan magis dan keberanian Harry, Ron dan Hermione."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"हैरी पौटर और रहस्यमयी तहखाना","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"61d51b36497560004227721d","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/61d51b36497560004227721d","author":"WiSpider","content":"Awesome 👍","created_at":"2022-01-05T04:14:46.346Z","updated_at":"2022-01-05T15:07:29.515Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"WiSpider","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"638132fb514c4a008789433e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/638132fb514c4a008789433e","author":"Nathan","content":"$11","created_at":"2022-11-25T21:26:19.504Z","updated_at":"2022-11-25T21:26:19.580Z","author_details":{"name":"Nathan","rating":8,"username":"TitanGusang","avatar_path":"/yHGV91jVzmqpFOtRSHF0avBZmPm.jpg"}},{"id":"64f42d0e3d43e0011b1c00fd","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/64f42d0e3d43e0011b1c00fd","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"This second book in JK Rowling's \"Harry Potter\" series sees our trio of wizarding weans start to develop a much closer relationship with each other; and we begin to realise the challenges young \"Harry\" (Daniel Radcliffe) is to face as he grows up. This is much more sinister than the opener; Alan Rickman's \"Prof. Snape\" starts to come into his own as his evil nemesis v Maggie Smith as his professional proponent and \"Dumbledore\" (Richard Harris) starts to develop more as a character too. I could possibly have done without \"Moaning Myrtle\" but the story is well adapted and moves along quickly, with a little more humour than the original too. Again, the score and effects are hugely complementary to what is simply a cracking fantasy adventure story.","created_at":"2023-09-03T06:51:58.913Z","updated_at":"2023-09-03T06:51:58.998Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.6854,"vote_count":22845,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.009,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":674,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","video":false,"overview":"When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.271,"vote_count":21865,"poster_path":"/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-16","vote_average":7.801,"backdrop_path":"/8f9dnOtpArDrOMEylpSN9Sc6fuz.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.7137,"vote_count":29166,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.7456,"vote_count":20501,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.5713,"vote_count":20531,"poster_path":"/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-08","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":14869,"adult":false,"title":"G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra","video":false,"overview":"From the Egyptian desert to deep below the polar ice caps, the elite G.I. JOE team uses the latest in next-generation spy and military equipment to fight the corrupt arms dealer Destro and the growing threat of the mysterious Cobra organization to prevent them from plunging the world into chaos.","genre_ids":[12,28,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2676,"vote_count":4838,"poster_path":"/mc9b25IAprHfsaOz0wTshOwGHcY.jpg","release_date":"2009-08-03","vote_average":5.787,"backdrop_path":"/jE5wVBRCGQzjHjvFUcYwGS4x0ux.jpg","original_title":"G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra","original_language":"en"},{"id":12444,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1","video":false,"overview":"Harry, Ron and Hermione walk away from their last year at Hogwarts to find and destroy the remaining Horcruxes, putting an end to Voldemort's bid for immortality. But with Harry's beloved Dumbledore dead and Voldemort's unscrupulous Death Eaters on the loose, the world is more dangerous than ever.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.1743,"vote_count":20107,"poster_path":"/iGoXIpQb7Pot00EEdwpwPajheZ5.jpg","release_date":"2010-11-17","vote_average":7.736,"backdrop_path":"/AqLcLsGGTzAjm3pCCq0CZCQrp6m.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1","original_language":"en"},{"id":12445,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2","video":false,"overview":"Harry, Ron and Hermione continue their quest to vanquish the evil Voldemort once and for all. Just as things begin to look hopeless for the young wizards, Harry discovers a trio of magical objects that endow him with powers to rival Voldemort's formidable skills.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.5285,"vote_count":21689,"poster_path":"/c54HpQmuwXjHq2C9wmoACjxoom3.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-12","vote_average":8.081,"backdrop_path":"/cbcpDn6XJaIGoOil1bKuskU8ds4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":64688,"adult":false,"title":"21 Jump Street","video":false,"overview":"When cops Schmidt and Jenko join the secret Jump Street unit, they use their youthful appearances to go undercover as high school students. They trade in their guns and badges for backpacks, and set out to shut down a dangerous drug ring. But, as time goes on, Schmidt and Jenko discover that high school is nothing like it was just a few years earlier -- and, what's more, they must again confront the teenage terror and anxiety they thought they had left behind.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.6684,"vote_count":10841,"poster_path":"/8v3Sqv9UcIUC4ebmpKWROqPBINZ.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-14","vote_average":6.884,"backdrop_path":"/d1ACwtoBygLKkGjCq9LUXnmcki.jpg","original_title":"21 Jump Street","original_language":"en"},{"id":1894,"adult":false,"title":"Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones","video":false,"overview":"Following an assassination attempt on Senator Padmé Amidala, Jedi Knights Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi investigate a mysterious plot into the heart of the Separatist movement and the beginning of the Clone Wars.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.463,"vote_count":14104,"poster_path":"/oZNPzxqM2s5DyVWab09NTQScDQt.jpg","release_date":"2002-05-15","vote_average":6.588,"backdrop_path":"/msYmRFJfXy0zsFd73PAEqdetKpO.jpg","original_title":"Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones","original_language":"en"},{"id":36657,"adult":false,"title":"X-Men","video":false,"overview":"Two mutants, Rogue and Wolverine, come to a private academy for their kind whose resident superhero team, the X-Men, must oppose a terrorist organization with similar powers.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.432,"vote_count":12002,"poster_path":"/bRDAc4GogyS9ci3ow7UnInOcriN.jpg","release_date":"2000-07-13","vote_average":7.01,"backdrop_path":"/3QUVzbcNyfGe3ocWkYAT8emK8Co.jpg","original_title":"X-Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":121,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","video":false,"overview":"Frodo Baggins and the other members of the Fellowship continue on their sacred quest to destroy the One Ring--but on separate paths. Their destinies lie at two towers--Orthanc Tower in Isengard, where the corrupt wizard Saruman awaits, and Sauron's fortress at Barad-dur, deep within the dark lands of Mordor. Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.6583,"vote_count":23458,"poster_path":"/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-18","vote_average":8.412,"backdrop_path":"/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","original_language":"en"},{"id":259316,"adult":false,"title":"Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them","video":false,"overview":"In 1926, Newt Scamander arrives at the Magical Congress of the United States of America with a magically expanded briefcase, which houses a number of dangerous creatures and their habitats. When the creatures escape from the briefcase, it sends the American wizarding authorities after Newt, and threatens to strain even further the state of magical and non-magical relations.","genre_ids":[14,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.5789,"vote_count":19514,"poster_path":"/fLsaFKExQt05yqjoAvKsmOMYvJR.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-16","vote_average":7.308,"backdrop_path":"/8Qsr8pvDL3s1jNZQ4HK1d1Xlvnh.jpg","original_title":"Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them","original_language":"en"},{"id":425,"adult":false,"title":"Ice Age","video":false,"overview":"Manny the mammoth, Sid the loquacious sloth, and Diego the sabre-toothed tiger go on a comical quest to return a human baby back to his father, across a world on the brink of an ice age.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.3219,"vote_count":14073,"poster_path":"/gLhHHZUzeseRXShoDyC4VqLgsNv.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-14","vote_average":7.368,"backdrop_path":"/8pwIhymsxfAVjrAE7syDjQULn37.jpg","original_title":"Ice Age","original_language":"en"},{"id":978870,"adult":false,"title":"Last Night of Amore","video":false,"overview":"On the night before retirement, police lieutenant Amore is called to investigate the off-duty death of his longtime partner, who fell prey of an illegal scheme Amore himself was secretly part of.","genre_ids":[53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.687,"vote_count":524,"poster_path":"/yKxmEfFrLjPLutpi7alffLOwMSj.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-09","vote_average":7.142,"backdrop_path":"/mUwtIH6Zl9tcl3Vo5IHoj5zG8MZ.jpg","original_title":"L'ultima notte di Amore","original_language":"it"},{"id":2501,"adult":false,"title":"The Bourne Identity","video":false,"overview":"Wounded to the brink of death and suffering from amnesia, Jason Bourne is rescued at sea by a fisherman. With nothing to go on but a Swiss bank account number, he starts to reconstruct his life, but finds that many people he encounters want him dead. However, Bourne realizes that he has the combat and mental skills of a world-class spy—but who does he work for?","genre_ids":[28,18,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.8282,"vote_count":9902,"poster_path":"/aP8swke3gmowbkfZ6lmNidu0y9p.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-14","vote_average":7.471,"backdrop_path":"/g1MFwTP8jQK5RM7Lz0ROZYkEZqI.jpg","original_title":"The Bourne Identity","original_language":"en"},{"id":557,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man","video":false,"overview":"After being bitten by a genetically altered spider at Oscorp, nerdy but endearing high school student Peter Parker is endowed with amazing powers to become the superhero known as Spider-Man.","genre_ids":[28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.067,"vote_count":20311,"poster_path":"/kjdJntyBeEvqm9w97QGBdxPptzj.jpg","release_date":"2002-05-01","vote_average":7.321,"backdrop_path":"/zQ8AxTPiCiS5nnwXpwTBPBHSaa5.jpg","original_title":"Spider-Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":58,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","video":false,"overview":"Jack's got a blood debt to pay: he owes his soul to the legendary Davy Jones, ghastly Ruler of the Ocean Depths.  But ever-crafty Jack isn't about to go down without a fight.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.454,"vote_count":16895,"poster_path":"/uXEqmloGyP7UXAiphJUu2v2pcuE.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-06","vote_average":7.374,"backdrop_path":"/vr6n6ZFUZvedvIlhfYcbCWcaKyW.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","original_language":"en"},{"id":12,"adult":false,"title":"Finding Nemo","video":false,"overview":"Nemo, an adventurous young clownfish, is unexpectedly taken from his Great Barrier Reef home to a dentist's office aquarium. It's up to his worrisome father Marlin and a friendly but forgetful fish Dory to bring Nemo home -- meeting vegetarian sharks, surfer dude turtles, hypnotic jellyfish, hungry seagulls, and more along the way.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.1674,"vote_count":20278,"poster_path":"/eHuGQ10FUzK1mdOY69wF5pGgEf5.jpg","release_date":"2003-05-30","vote_average":7.817,"backdrop_path":"/eCynaAOgYYiw5yN5lBwz3IxqvaW.jpg","original_title":"Finding Nemo","original_language":"en"},{"id":608,"adult":false,"title":"Men in Black II","video":false,"overview":"Kay and Jay reunite to provide our best, last and only line of defense against a sinister seductress who levels the toughest challenge yet to the MIB's untarnished mission statement – protecting Earth from the scum of the universe. It's been four years since the alien-seeking agents averted an intergalactic disaster of epic proportions. Now it's a race against the clock as Jay must convince Kay – who not only has absolutely no memory of his time spent with the MIB, but is also the only living person left with the expertise to save the galaxy – to reunite with the MIB before the earth submits to ultimate destruction.","genre_ids":[28,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.5485,"vote_count":10481,"poster_path":"/enA22EPyzc2WQ1VVyY7zxresQQr.jpg","release_date":"2002-07-03","vote_average":6.383,"backdrop_path":"/o1l6OCqA3pYDZHIc5L1s7CEzCMv.jpg","original_title":"Men in Black II","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":162,"adult":false,"title":"Edward Scissorhands","video":false,"overview":"A small suburban town receives a visit from a castaway unfinished science experiment named Edward.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"popularity":9.0172,"vote_count":13586,"poster_path":"/e0FqKFvGPdQNWG8tF9cZBtev9Em.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-07","vote_average":7.719,"backdrop_path":"/uNLIMPxknsV4n3IAEDpS1iqF5dm.jpg","original_title":"Edward Scissorhands","original_language":"en"},{"id":165,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future Part II","video":false,"overview":"Marty and Doc are at it again as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"popularity":7.1854,"vote_count":13683,"poster_path":"/YBawEsTkUZBDajKbd5LiHkmMGf.jpg","release_date":"1989-11-22","vote_average":7.775,"backdrop_path":"/w6tPctxWAsHoQXeKxxNOT6lYKpx.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":763577,"adult":false,"title":"Spiritpact","video":false,"overview":"Yang Jinghua, a young heir to a family of exorcists, is left struggling alone after his parents’ deaths. Barely surviving, he encounters the wealthy and skilled exorcist Duanmu Xi while trying to fend off a spirit. After a fatal accident, Yang awakens to find himself in a contract with Duanmu Xi, marking the start of his new life.","genre_ids":[14],"popularity":0.2472,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gQfa44P8piUHJ8A7bP6j0PXBNEy.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-11","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":"/6P5Y2u2HrnOrTVQXTNDUNsJpSiS.jpg","original_title":"灵契","original_language":"zh"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesis, Ernst Stravro Blofeld, to a mountaintop retreat in the Swiss Alps, where he is training an army of beautiful, lethal women.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.3271,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/m3KfbxvqaiAvRJ6MpguA3GuLdDQ.jpg","release_date":"1969-12-18","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/58pMrmwwcKamJIdjUlinE6QX1Fs.jpg","original_title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":22.7137,"vote_count":29166,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":15.6854,"vote_count":22845,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.009,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":674,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","video":false,"overview":"When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":17.271,"vote_count":21865,"poster_path":"/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-16","vote_average":7.801,"backdrop_path":"/8f9dnOtpArDrOMEylpSN9Sc6fuz.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.5713,"vote_count":20531,"poster_path":"/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-08","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"},{"id":756,"adult":false,"title":"Fantasia","video":false,"overview":"Walt Disney's timeless masterpiece is an extravaganza of sight and sound! See the music come to life, hear the pictures burst into song and experience the excitement that is Fantasia over and over again.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":4.2512,"vote_count":3268,"poster_path":"/5m9njnidjR0syG2gpVPVgcEMB2X.jpg","release_date":"1940-11-13","vote_average":7.342,"backdrop_path":"/lyzI5uFJC2E7sIYCCdaU0oZkDw2.jpg","original_title":"Fantasia","original_language":"en"},{"id":766,"adult":false,"title":"Army of Darkness","video":false,"overview":"Ash, a handsome, shotgun-toting, chainsaw-armed department store clerk, is time warped backwards into England's Dark Ages, where he romances a beauty and faces legions of the undead.","genre_ids":[14,27,35],"popularity":4.5693,"vote_count":3433,"poster_path":"/xsgTuAtR2zSH8Umg3jWZcZjlDpe.jpg","release_date":"1992-10-31","vote_average":7.261,"backdrop_path":"/5RPXs9g0sZ9Woo4pNLxdXdge7tc.jpg","original_title":"Army of Darkness","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":13.7456,"vote_count":20501,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.682,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":772,"adult":false,"title":"Home Alone 2: Lost in New York","video":false,"overview":"Instead of flying to Florida with his folks, Kevin ends up alone in New York, where he gets a hotel room with his dad's credit card—despite problems from a clerk and meddling bellboy. But when Kevin runs into his old nemeses, the Wet Bandits, he's determined to foil their plans to rob a toy store on Christmas Eve.","genre_ids":[35,10751,12],"popularity":10.9577,"vote_count":10446,"poster_path":"/9CAkQ9nfrDaIAyncWndwg0tfC8g.jpg","release_date":"1992-11-15","vote_average":6.779,"backdrop_path":"/8fnYJPoXxwAN4valDLgz2whMGTH.jpg","original_title":"Home Alone 2: Lost in New York","original_language":"en"},{"id":2006,"adult":false,"title":"Bell, Book and Candle","video":false,"overview":"Gillian Holroyd, a modern-day witch, becomes smitten with her handsome upstairs neighbor, Shep Henderson. Using her magical powers, she casts a love spell on him, only to face unexpected complications when genuine feelings emerge, threatening her supernatural abilities.","genre_ids":[35,14,10749],"popularity":0.897,"vote_count":239,"poster_path":"/z3MLtVFPT2wIkKCBSE2yBgDmeXI.jpg","release_date":"1958-12-25","vote_average":6.471,"backdrop_path":"/y5e5MTZtbMesmJ7EYgBdlceMcWq.jpg","original_title":"Bell, Book and Candle","original_language":"en"},{"id":879,"adult":false,"title":"Hook","video":false,"overview":"The boy who wasn't supposed to grow up—Peter Pan—does just that, becoming a soulless corporate lawyer whose workaholism could cost him his wife and kids. During his trip to see Granny Wendy in London, the vengeful Capt. Hook kidnaps Peter's kids and forces Peter to return to Neverland.","genre_ids":[12,14,35,10751],"popularity":7.3012,"vote_count":5619,"poster_path":"/a6rB1lGXoGms7gWxRfJneQmAjNV.jpg","release_date":"1991-04-10","vote_average":6.838,"backdrop_path":"/39OxcFZjX4uc6vYzexUh5qXghxE.jpg","original_title":"Hook","original_language":"en"},{"id":920,"adult":false,"title":"Cars","video":false,"overview":"Lightning McQueen, a hotshot rookie race car driven to succeed, discovers that life is about the journey, not the finish line, when he finds himself unexpectedly detoured in the sleepy Route 66 town of Radiator Springs. On route across the country to the big Piston Cup Championship in California to compete against two seasoned pros, McQueen gets to know the town's offbeat characters.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751],"popularity":9.3041,"vote_count":14884,"poster_path":"/2Touk3m5gzsqr1VsvxypdyHY5ci.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-08","vote_average":7.021,"backdrop_path":"/sd4xN5xi8tKRPrJOWwNiZEile7f.jpg","original_title":"Cars","original_language":"en"},{"id":927,"adult":false,"title":"Gremlins","video":false,"overview":"After receiving an exotic small animal as a Christmas gift, a young man inadvertently breaks three important rules concerning his new pet, which unleashes a horde of malevolently mischievous creatures on a small town.","genre_ids":[14,27,35],"popularity":7.416,"vote_count":6858,"poster_path":"/6m0F7fsXjQvUbCZrPWcJNrjvIui.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-08","vote_average":7.14,"backdrop_path":"/5UX6M0aEphiW6Xmy5rpYX75glbo.jpg","original_title":"Gremlins","original_language":"en"},{"id":421760,"adult":false,"title":"A Heavenly Christmas","video":false,"overview":"Upon her untimely death, a workaholic finds herself in training to be a Christmas Angel in Heaven. Despite being the worst recruit in the history of Christmas, she’s assigned a hard luck case. As she’s forced to help solve his problems, she’ll start to discover the meaning of Christmas and maybe even fall in love along the way.","genre_ids":[18,10749,14,10770],"popularity":0.3947,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/tFXXlWKUaD1CRC4g2lpaBYJTkl.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-26","vote_average":6.086,"backdrop_path":"/f8QEmuRWXXKq8nG6U0LkQUwwacw.jpg","original_title":"A Heavenly Christmas","original_language":"en"},{"id":251733,"adult":false,"title":"The Brides of Sodom","video":false,"overview":"In a post apocalyptic world where vampires and witches rule, a male vampire falls in love with a human man, and wants to make him immortal.","genre_ids":[14,27,878],"popularity":0.1735,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/q7XNxsqiONJlFQNicLfpc3yrf98.jpg","release_date":"2013-01-28","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/zZ6horsMHGnFk