9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione's magical abilities and courage."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/107101/harry-potter-and-the-chamber-of-secrets"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione's magical abilities and courage."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/107101/harry-potter-and-the-chamber-of-secrets"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sdEOH0992YZ0QSxgXNIGLq1ToUi.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on